The paper deals with vehicle re-identification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also introduces novel attention modules and normalization techniques, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.MM), deep learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper addresses adversarial conditions, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
